#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_color_blocks_2
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Environmental protection is the practice of safeguarding the natural "
"world from harmful human activities and preserving ecosystems for future "
"generations. It involves efforts to reduce pollution, conserve biodiversity, "
"and sustainably manage natural resources such as air, water, and soil.\n"
"        <br/>"
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        La protection environnementale consiste à protéger le monde naturel "
"des activités humaines nuisibles et à préserver les écosystèmes pour les "
"générations futures. Elle implique des efforts pour réduire la pollution, "
"conserver la biodiversité et gérer durablement les ressources naturelles "
"telles que l'air, l'eau et le sol.\n"
"        <br/>"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_sidegrid
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Every step we take towards sustainability is a commitment to "
"preserving nature's beauty and resources, for today and tomorrow."
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Chaque mesure que nous prenons en faveur du développement durable "
"est un engagement en faveur de la préservation de la beauté et des "
"ressources de la nature, pour aujourd'hui et pour demain."

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_numbers_list
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        From carbon footprint reduction to renewable energy adoption and "
"biodiversity preservation, our key milestones reflect our commitment to "
"creating a sustainable future for all."
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        De la réduction de l'empreinte carbone à l'adoption des énergies "
"renouvelables en passant par la préservation de la biodiversité, nos "
"principaux accomplissements reflètent notre engagement à créer un avenir "
"durable pour tous."

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_numbers_list
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h2-fs\">1.2 Billion</span><br/>\n"
"        Liters of water saved"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"h2-fs\">1,2 milliard</span><br/>\n"
"        De litres d’eau économisés"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_numbers_list
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h2-fs\">2 Million</span><br/>\n"
"        Trees Planted"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"h2-fs\">2 millions</span><br/>\n"
"        D’arbres plantés"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_numbers_list
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h2-fs\">45%</span><br/>\n"
"        Reduction in carbon emissions"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"h2-fs\">45 %</span><br/>\n"
"        De réduction des émissions de CO₂"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_numbers_list
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h2-fs\">500,000</span><br/>\n"
"        Tons of materials recycled"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"h2-fs\">500 000</span><br/>\n"
"        Tonnes de matériaux recyclés"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_numbers_list
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h2-fs\">60%</span><br/>\n"
"        Renewable Energy usage"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"h2-fs\">60 %</span><br/>\n"
"        D’énergie renouvelable utilisée"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_numbers_list
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h2-fs\">85%</span><br/>\n"
"        Waste diversion rate"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"h2-fs\">85 %</span><br/>\n"
"        De taux de détournement des déchets"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_color_blocks_2
msgid "A Call for Environmental Protection"
msgstr "Un appel à la protection de l'environnement"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_freegrid
msgid "Be Part of the Change"
msgstr "Participez au changement"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_treehouse.field_theme_utils__display_name
msgid "Display Name"
msgstr "Nom d'affichage"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_treehouse.field_theme_utils__id
msgid "ID"
msgstr "ID"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_freegrid
msgid ""
"Join us in our mission to protect the environment and promote sustainable "
"development. We focus on creating a greener future through innovative "
"ecological solutions."
msgstr ""
"Participez à notre mission de protection de l'environnement et de promotion "
"du développement durable. Nous nous efforçons de créer un avenir plus vert "
"grâce à des solutions écologiques innovantes."

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_numbers_list
msgid "Key milestones in our environmental impact"
msgstr "Les grandes dates de notre impact sur l'environnement"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_references
msgid "More details <i class=\"fa fa-long-arrow-right ms-2\"/>"
msgstr "Plus de détails <i class=\"fa fa-long-arrow-right ms-2\"/>"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_sidegrid
msgid "Protect <br/>the planet <br/>for future generations"
msgstr "Protégez <br/>la planète <br/>pour les générations futures"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_freegrid
msgid "Sustainability for a Better Tomorrow"
msgstr "Le développement durable pour un avenir meilleur"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model:ir.model,name:theme_treehouse.model_theme_utils
msgid "Theme Utils"
msgstr "Thèmes utiles"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_references
msgid ""
"Together, we collaborate with leading organizations committed to protecting "
"the environment and building a greener future."
msgstr ""
"Ensemble, nous collaborons avec des organisations de premier plan qui "
"s'engagent à protéger l'environnement et à construire un avenir plus vert."
